  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>About This Game</strong></h2>Monsters in the abyss are awakening, and the twinworld is slowly collapsing. Create unique builds with various weapons, items, and upgrades, explore the twinworld, and survive waves of monsters. Can you survive until the end and uncover the secrets of the twinworld?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934100/extras/6b53a65ed7f3e9752da500df67d42526.poster.avif?t=1721369296\" width=622 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934100/extras/6b53a65ed7f3e9752da500df67d42526.webm?t=1721369296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934100/extras/6b53a65ed7f3e9752da500df67d42526.mp4?t=1721369296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Attack monsters with all the weapons you can find, throw a basketball, swing a guitar, or summon a magic book! There are many unexpected and wonderful weapons and jewelry in the game, even a wig has its unique role. Depending on the characteristics of the monsters, use these items and upgrades to create dynamic builds and grow into a powerful investigator.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934100/extras/7e02fb3d4399ec4c8e9bdc0ff8e1908a.poster.avif?t=1721369296\" width=622 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934100/extras/7e02fb3d4399ec4c8e9bdc0ff8e1908a.webm?t=1721369296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934100/extras/7e02fb3d4399ec4c8e9bdc0ff8e1908a.mp4?t=1721369296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>6 characters with special skill available  </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>50+ weapons and 60+ jewelry to choose from (chainsaw, SMGs, RPG or sticks, even basketball and guitar)</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Collect materials to gain experience and choose skill when upgrade</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Get items from the shop and enhance your strength before game start</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Manual aiming weapons by default with a auto-firing option</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Quickly runs (10 minutes per round at most)</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>About This Game</strong></h2>Monsters in the abyss are awakening, and the twinworld is slowly collapsing. Create unique builds with various weapons, items, and upgrades, explore the twinworld, and survive waves of monsters. Can you survive until the end and uncover the secrets of the twinworld?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934100/extras/6b53a65ed7f3e9752da500df67d42526.poster.avif?t=1721369296\" width=622 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934100/extras/6b53a65ed7f3e9752da500df67d42526.webm?t=1721369296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934100/extras/6b53a65ed7f3e9752da500df67d42526.mp4?t=1721369296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Attack monsters with all the weapons you can find, throw a basketball, swing a guitar, or summon a magic book! There are many unexpected and wonderful weapons and jewelry in the game, even a wig has its unique role. Depending on the characteristics of the monsters, use these items and upgrades to create dynamic builds and grow into a powerful investigator.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934100/extras/7e02fb3d4399ec4c8e9bdc0ff8e1908a.poster.avif?t=1721369296\" width=622 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934100/extras/7e02fb3d4399ec4c8e9bdc0ff8e1908a.webm?t=1721369296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934100/extras/7e02fb3d4399ec4c8e9bdc0ff8e1908a.mp4?t=1721369296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>6 characters with special skill available  </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>50+ weapons and 60+ jewelry to choose from (chainsaw, SMGs, RPG or sticks, even basketball and guitar)</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Collect materials to gain experience and choose skill when upgrade</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Get items from the shop and enhance your strength before game start</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Manual aiming weapons by default with a auto-firing option</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Quickly runs (10 minutes per round at most)</li></ul>",
